  <h3><span class="author">
    
          JF
    
  </span> <span class="date">03 Jan 06</span></h3>
  <p><em>Why MT when Wordpress is free? Just curious I used to use MT long ago but switched to WP when MT started charging licensing fees.</em></p>

<p>I don&#8217;t believe in switching to something just because it&#8217;s free. I&#8217;m happy to reward companies that produce nice software. I have my issues with MT, but it&#8217;s served us well. Plus, the time it would take to switch over to WP and get acquainted with it isn&#8217;t free.</p>

<p>One day we may roll our own blog tool that better serves us, but we&#8217;re not going to chase this tool or that tool because one costs less than the other.</p>
  </div>
  
