  <h3><span class="author">
    
          Anonymous Coward
    
  </span> <span class="date">04 Jan 06</span></h3>
  <p>jEdit is a free, powerful text editor, which runs on Macs, Windows, and Unix. It&#8217;s written in Java, and it&#8217;s quite well done. It is under active development, and there are lots of plugins to expand functionality. I prefer its Ruby tools to those in Eclipse.</p>
  </div>
  
